      <title>马斯克发表德国言论后，特斯拉在波兰面临抵制呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/tesla-faces-call-for-boycott-in-poland-after-musk-s-germany-remarks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克表示，特斯拉汽车“过多关注过去的罪行”，明显是指德国在纳粹统治下的战争暴行。随后，一位波兰政府部长呼吁抵制特斯拉汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/tesla-faces-call-for-boycott-in-poland-after-musk-s-germany-remarks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 15:37:59 GMT</pubDate>
